# Default Aasimar																																
Racial Trait ~ Aasimar	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Aasimar Trait|AUTOMATIC|Aasimar ~ Darkvision|Aasimar ~ Celestial Resistance|Aasimar ~ Healing Hands|Aasimar ~ Light Bearer	ABILITY:Aasimar Trait|AUTOMATIC|Aasimar ~ Celestial Revelation|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3								SOURCEPAGE:PHB																																

Aasimar size	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Medium (about 4-7 feet tall) or Small (about 2-4 feet tall), chosen when you select this species	KEY:Aasimar ~ Aasimar Size									BONUS:VAR|POOL_Racial_Size|1																		SOURCEPAGE:PHB 
Celestial Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have resistance to necrotic damage and radiant damage.	KEY:Aasimar ~ Celestial Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB 
Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 60 feet.	KEY:Aasimar ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Healing Hands	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:As a Magic action, you touch a creature and roll a number of D4s equal to your Proficiency Bonus. The creature regains a number of Hit Points equal to the total rolled. Once you use this trait, you can't use it again until you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Aasimar ~ Healing Hands															SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Light Bearer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You know th e Light cantrip . Charisma is your spellcasting ability for it.	KEY:Aasimar ~ Light Bearer													SPELLS:Aasimar Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Light,SpellDC_CHA														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Celestial Revelation	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aasimar Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you reach 3rd character level 3, you can transform as a Bonus Action using one of the options below (choose the option each time you transform). The transformation lasts for 1 minute or until you end it (no action required). Once you transform, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest. Once on each of your turns before the transformation ends, you can dea l extra damage to one target when you deal damage to it with an attack or a spell. The extra da mage equals your Proficienc y Bonus, and the extra damage's type is either Necrotic for Necrotic Shroud or Radiant fo r Heave nly Wings and Inner Radiance.	KEY:Aasimar ~ Celestial Revelation						BONUS:VAR|POOL_Celestial_Revelation|1									SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Heavenly Wings	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Celestial Revelation	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Two spectral wings sprout from your back temporarily. Until the transformation ends, you have a Fly Speed equal to your Speed.	KEY:Celestial Revelation ~ Heavenly Wings													MOVECLONE:Walk,Fly,*1														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Inner Radiance	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Celestial Revelation	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Searing light temporarily radiates from your eyes and mouth. For the duration , you shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, and at the end of each of your turns, each creature within 10 feet of you takes Radiant damage equal to your Proficiency Bonus.	KEY:Celestial Revelation ~ Inner Radiance																									SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Necrotic Shroud	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Celestial Revelation	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your eyes briefly become pools of darkness, and flightless wings sprout from your back temporarily. Creatures other than your allies within 10 feet of you must succeed on a Charisma saving throw (DC 8 plus your Charisma modifier and Proficiency Bonus) or have the Frightened condition until the end of your next turn.	KEY:Celestial Revelation ~ Necrotic Shroud	DESC:DC %1.|NecroticShroudDC	DEFINE:NecroticShroudDC|0				BONUS:VAR|NecroticShroudDC|SpellDC_CHA																			SOURCEPAGE:PHB

# Default Dragonborn
Racial Trait ~ Dragonborn	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Dragonborn Trait|AUTOMATIC|Dragonborn ~ Draconic Ancestry|Dragonborn ~ Darkvision	ABILITY:Dragonborn Trait|AUTOMATIC|Dragonborn ~ Draconic Flight|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5								SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Draconic Ancestry	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your lineage stems from a dragon progenitor. Choose the kind of dragon from the Draconic Ancestors table. Your choice affects yo ur Breath Weapon and Damage Resistance traits as well as your appearance.	KEY:Dragonborn ~ Draconic Ancestry						BONUS:VAR|POOL_Draconic_Ancestry|1																					SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 60 feet.	KEY:Dragonborn ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Draconic Flight	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you reach character level 5, you can channel draconic magic to give yourself temporary flight. As a Bonus Action, you sprout spectral wings on your back that last for 10 minutes or until you retract the wings (no action required) or have the Incapacitated condition. During that time, you have a Fly Speed equal to your Speed. Your wings appear to be made of the same energy as your Breath Weapon. Once you use this trait, you can't use it again until you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Dragonborn ~ Draconic Flight													MOVECLONE:Walk,Fly,*1														SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Breath Weapon	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can replace one of your attacks with an exhalation of magical energy in either a 15-foot Cone or a 30-foot Line that is 5 feet wide (choose the shape each time). Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw (DC 8 plus your Constitution modifier and Proficiency Bonus). On a failed save, a creature takes 1d10 Acid damage. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage. This damage increases by 1dlO when you reach character levels 5 (2d10), 11 (3d10), and 17 (4d10). You can use this Breath Weapon a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Draconic Ancestry ~ Black ~ Breath Weapon	DESC:DC %1.|BreathWeaponDC	DEFINE:BreathWEaponDC|0			BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDC|SpellDC_CHA																						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Breath Weapon	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can replace one of your attacks with an exhalation of magical energy in either a 15-foot Cone or a 30-foot Line that is 5 feet wide (choose the shape each time). Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw (DC 8 plus your Constitution modifier and Proficiency Bonus). On a failed save, a creature takes 1d10 Lightning damage. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage. This damage increases by 1dlO when you reach character levels 5 (2d10), 11 (3d10), and 17 (4d10). You can use this Breath Weapon a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Draconic Ancestry ~ Blue ~ Breath Weapon	DESC:DC %1.|BreathWeaponDC	DEFINE:BreathWEaponDC|0			BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDC|SpellDC_CHA																						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Breath Weapon	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragonborn Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can replace one of your attacks with an exhalation of magical energy in either a 15-foot Cone or a 30-foot Line that is 5 feet wide (choose the shape each time). Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw (DC 8 plus your Constitution modifier and Proficiency Bonus). On a failed save, a creature takes 1d10 Fire damage. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage. This damage increases by 1dlO when you reach character levels 5 (2d10), 11 (3d10), and 17 (4d10). You can use this Breath Weapon a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Draconic Ancestry ~ Brass ~ Breath Weapon	DESC:DC %1.|BreathWeaponDC	DEFINE:BreathWEaponDC|0			BONUS:VAR|BreathWeaponDC|SpellDC_CHA																						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
