# Default Dwarf
Racial Trait ~ Dwarf	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Dwarf Trait|AUTOMATIC|Dwarf ~ Darkvision|Dwarf ~ Dwarven Resilience|Dwarf ~ Dwarven Toughness|Dwarf ~ Stonecunning	

Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dwarf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 120 feet.	KEY:Dwarf ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|120|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Dwarven Resilience	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dwarf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Resistance to Poison damage. You also have Advantage on saving throws you make to avoid or end the Poisoned condition.	KEY:Dwarf ~ Dwarven Resilience																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Dwarven Toughness	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dwarf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your Hit Point maximum increases by 1, and it increases by 1 again whenever you gain a level.	KEY:Dwarf ~ Dwarven Toughness																BONUS:HP|CURRENTMAX|HD																					SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Stonecunning	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dwarf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:As a Bonus Action , you gain Tremorsense with a range of 60 feet for 10 minutes. You must be on a stone surface or touching a stone surface to use this Tremorsense. The stone can be natural or worked. You can use this Bonus Action a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Dwarf ~ Stonecunning																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

# Default Elf																																
Racial Trait ~ Elf	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Elf Trait|AUTOMATIC|Elf ~ Darkvision|Elf ~ Elven Lineage|Elf ~ Fey Ancestry|Elf ~ Keen Senses|Elf ~ Trance

Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Elf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 60 feet.	KEY:Elf ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Elven Lineage	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Elf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You are part of a lineage that grants you supernatural abilities. Choose a lineage from the Elven Lineages table. You gain the level 1 benefit of that lineage. When you reach character levels 3 and 5, you learn a higher-level spell, as shown on the table. You always have that spell prepared. You can cast it once without a spell slot, and you regain the ability to cast it in that way when you finish a Long Rest. You can also cast the spell using any spell slots you have of the appropriate level. Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma is your spellcasting ability for the spells you cast with this trait (choose the ability when you select the lineage).	KEY:Elf ~ Elven Lineage						BONUS:VAR|POOL_Elven_Lineage|1																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Fey Ancestry	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Elf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Advantage on saving throws you make to avoid or end the Charmed condition.	KEY:Elf ~ Fey Ancestry																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Keen Senses	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Elf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have proficiency in the Insight, Perception, or Survival skill.	KEY:Elf ~ Keen Senses													BONUS:VAR|POOL_Elf_Keen_Senses|1														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Trances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Elf Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You don't need to sleep, and magic can't put you to sleep. You can finish a Long Rest in 4 hours if you spend those hours in a trancelike meditation, during which you retain consciousness.	KEY:Elf ~ Trances																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Drow	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Elven Lineage	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your elven ancestry is Drow.	KEY:Elven Lineage ~ Drow						BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|120|TYPE=Base			TEMPLATE:Elven Lineage ~ Drow	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Dancing Light	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Faerie Fire|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Darkness|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
High Elf	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Elven Lineage	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your elven ancestry is High Elf.	KEY:Elven Lineage ~ High Elf									BONUS:VAR|POOL_Wizard_Cantrips|1	TEMPLATE:Elven Lineage ~ High Elf	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Detect Magic|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Misty Step|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Wood Elf	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Elven Lineage	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your elven ancestry is Wood Elf.	KEY:Elven Lineage ~ Wood Elf									BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE.Walk|5	TEMPLATE:Elven Lineage ~ Wood Elf	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Druidcraft	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Longstrider|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Elf Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Pass Without Trace|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	SOURCEPAGE:PHB

