Giant Ancestry	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Goliath Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You are descended from Giants. Choose one of the following benefits- a supernatural boon from your ancestry; you can use the chosen benefit a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you fin ish a Long Rest.	KEY:Goliath ~ Giant Ancestry						BONUS:VAR|POOL_Giant_Ancestry|1																					SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Large Form	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Goliath Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Star ting at ch aracter level 5, you can change your size to Large as a Bonus Action if you're in a big enough space. This transformation lasts for 10 minutes or until you end it (no action required). For that duration , you have Advantage on Strength checks, and you r Speed increases by 10 feet. Once you use this trait, you can't use it again until you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Goliath ~ Large Form																							SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Powerful Build	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Goliath Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Advantage on any saving throw you make to end the Grappled condition. You also count as one size larger when determining your carrying capacity.	KEY:Goliath ~ Powerful Build					BONUS:VAR|LoadScoreMult|1	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Simple|PCSIZE|1	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Martial|PCSIZE|1	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Exotic|PCSIZE|1																		SOURCEPAGE:PHB	

Cloud's Jaunt	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:As a Bonus Action, you magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see.	KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Cloud's Jaunt	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Cloud Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Fire's Burn	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you hit a target with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can also deal ldlO Fire damage to that target.	KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Fire's Burn	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Fire Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Frost's Chill	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you hit a target with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can also deal ld6 Cold damage to that target and reduce its Speed by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.	KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Frost's Chill	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Frost Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Hill's Tumble	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you hit a Large or smaller creature with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can give that target the Prone condition. KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Hill's Tumble	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Hill Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Stone's Endurance	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you take damage, you can take a Reaction to roll 1d12. Add your Constitution modifier to the number rolled and reduce the damage by that total.	KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Stone's Endurance	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Stone Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB	
Storm's Thunder	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Giant Ancestry	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you take damage from a creature w ithin 60 feet of you, you can take a Reac tion to deal 1d8 Thunder damage to that creature.	KEY:Giant Ancestry ~ Storm's Thunder	DESC:&nl; %1/Long Rest|ProficiencyBonus												TEMPLATE:Giant Ancestry ~ Storm Giant														SOURCEPAGE:PHB

# Default Halfling
