Adrenaline Rush	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You can take the Dash action as a Bonus Action. When you do so, you gain a number of Temporary Hit Points equal to your Proficiency Bonus. You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Short or Long Rest.	KEY:Orc ~ Adrenaline Rush																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 120 feet. KEY:Orc ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|120|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Relentless Endurance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you are reduced to 0 Hit Points but not killed outright, you can drop to 1 Hit Point instead. Once you use this trait, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Orc ~ Relentless Endurance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

# Default Tiefling
Racial Trait ~ Tiefling	CATEGORY:Internal																						ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Tiefling Size|Tiefling ~ Darkvision|Tiefling ~ Fiendish Legacy|Tiefling ~ Otherwordly Presence

Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 60 feet. KEY:Tiefling ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|60|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB	
Fiendish Legacy	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You are the recipient of a legacy that grants you supernatural abilities. Choose a legacy from the Fiendish Legacies table. You gain the level 1 benefit of the chosen legacy. When you reach character levels 3 and 5, you learn a higher-level spell, as shown on the table. You always have that spell prepared. You can cast it once without a spell slot, and you regain the ability to cast it in that way when you finish a Long Rest. You can also cast the spell using any spell slots you have of the appropriate level. Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma is your spellcasting ability for the spells you cast with this trait (choose the ability when you select the legacy).	KEY:Tiefling ~ Fiendish Legacy						BONUS:VAR|POOL_Fiendish_Legacy|1																					SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Otherwordly Presence	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You know the Thaumaturgy cantrip. When you cast it with this trait, the spell uses the same spellcasting ability you use for your Fiendish Legacy trait.	KEY:Tiefling ~ Otherworldly Presence													SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Thaumaturgy														SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Poison Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have resistance to Poison damage.	KEY:Tiefling ~ Poison Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Necrotic Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have resistance to Necrotic damage.	KEY:Tiefling ~ Necrotic Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Fire Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have resistance to Fire damage.	KEY:Tiefling ~ Fire Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Abyssal	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Fiendish Legacy	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your fiendish legacy is Abyssal.	KEY:Fiendish Legacy ~ Abyssal						TEMPLATE:Fiendish Legacy ~ Abyssal	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Poison Spray	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Ray of Sickness|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Hold Person|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Poison Resistance	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Chtonic	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Fiendish Legacy	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your fiendish legacy is Chthonic.	KEY:Fiendish Legacy ~ Chthonic						TEMPLATE:Fiendish Legacy ~ Chthonic	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Chill Touch	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|False Life|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Ray of Enfeeblement|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Necrotic Resistance	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Infernal	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Fiendish Legacy	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your fiendish legacy is Infernal.	KEY:Fiendish Legacy ~ Infernal						TEMPLATE:Fiendish Legacy ~ Infernal	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Fire Bolt	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Hellish Rebuke|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Darkness|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Fire Resistance	SOURCEPAGE:PHB

###Block: Familiars
Telepathic Connection	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.FamiliarTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:While your familiar is within 100 feet of you, you can communicate with it telepathically. Additionally, as a Bonus Action, you can see through the familiar's eyes and hear what it hears until the start of your next turn, gaining the benefits of any special senses it has. Finally, when you cast a spell with a range of touch , your familiar can deliver the touch. Your familiar must be within 100 feet of you , and it must take a Reaction to del iver the touch when you cast the spell.	KEY:Familiar ~ Telepathic Connection																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

