Beast's Strike	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.BeastOfTheLandRacialTrait.SpecialAttack	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Melee Attack Roll: Bonus equals your spell attack modifier, reach 5 ft. Hit: ld8 + 2 plus your Wisdom m od ifier Bludgeon ing, Piercing, or Slashing damage (your choice when you summon the beast). If the beast moved at least 20 feet straight toward the target before the hit, the target takes an extra 1d6 damage of the same type, and the target has the Prone condition if it is a Large or smaller creature.	KEY:Beast of the Land ~ Beast's Strike																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

