Life Bond	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.OtherworldlySteedRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you regain Hit Points from a level 1+ spell, the steed regains the same number of Hit Points if you're within 5 feet of it .	KEY:Otherworldly Steed ~ Life Bond																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Fell Glare	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.OtherworldlySteedRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Wisdom Saving Throw: DC equals your spell save DC, one creature within 60 feet the steed can see. Failure: The target has the Frightened condition until the end of your next turn.	KEY:Otherworldly Steed ~ Fell Glare	ASPECT:NAME|Fell Glare (Recharges after a Long Rest) 																										SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Fey Step	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.OtherworldlySteedRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The steed teleports , along with its rider, to an unoccupied space of your choice up to 60 feet away from itself.	KEY:Otherworldly Steed ~ Fey Step	ASPECT:NAME|Fey Step (Recharges after a Long Rest) 																										SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Healing Touch	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.OtherworldlySteedRacialTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:O ne creature within 5 feet of the steed regains a number of Hit Points equal to 2d8 plus the spell's level.	KEY:Otherworldly Steed ~ Healing Touch	ASPECT:NAME|Healing Touch (Recharges after a Long Rest) 																										SOURCEPAGE:PHB
